3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper deals with a system of two base stations acting as relay nodes and cooperating with each other, which is a typical topic in systems and control. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper discusses the downlink of a cloud radio access network, which is related to multimedia transmission. 
5. cs.CC (Computational Complexity) - Although not the main focus of the paper, the analysis of the coding schemes involves complexity considerations, which could be relevant to computational complexity.
